# Sheet Name: JetBrains Rider Shortcuts
# App: /Applications/Rider.app
# Keymap: IntelliJ (default)

[Search & Navigation]
> ⇧⇧ and ⌃⌃ mean double-tap the key.
⇧⇧              Search Everywhere
⌘⇧A             Find Action
⌃⌃              Run Anything
⌘E              Recent Files
⌘⇧O             Go to File
⌘⌥O             Go to Symbol
⌘L              Go to Line/Column
⌘B              Go to Declaration or Usages
⌘⌥B             Go to Implementation(s)
⌘⇧B             Go to Type Declaration
⌘U              Go to Super Method
⌘[              Navigate Back
⌘]              Navigate Forward
⌥F1             Select In...
⌃⇧↓             Next Method
⌃⇧↑             Previous Method

